SQL_STMT_U.val: select B.INVS_INVO_NO, B.INVS_BUYERID, B.INVS_RECEIVABLENUMBER, B.INVS_ISSUEDATE, B.INVS_DUEDATE, B.INVS_EXPECTEDPAYMENTDATE, B.INVS_CURRENCY, B.INVS_CERTIFIEDAMOUNT, B.INVS_ADMNO, B.INVS_CLNTNO, B.INVS_SUPPLIERID, B.INVS_DEBC_NO, A.INSP_FINANCE_PERC, A.INSP_FINANCEDATE, A.INSP_AMOUNT, F.CLNT110_NAME1, G.DEBC_DEBH from :1/INSP A join :1/INVS B on B.INVS_INVO_NO = A.INSP_INVO_NO join :1/SCPC E on E.SCPC_ADMNO = :2 and E.SCPC_CLNTNO = :5 and E.SCPC_NEW = 'N' join :1/CLNT F on CLNT101_ADMNO = INVS_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = INVS_CLNTNO join :1/DEBC G on DEBC_NO = INVS_DEBC_NO where A.INSP_PARTICIPANT_ADMNO = :2 and A.INSP_PARTICIPANT_CLNTNO = :3 and A.INSP_SCFP_NO = :4 and A.INSP_FINALPAYMENTDATE is null and B.INVS_INVO_NO not in (select C.SBSD_INVO_NO from :1/SBSD C cross join :1/SBSH D where C.SBSD_INVO_NO = B.INVS_INVO_NO and D.SBSH_ID = C.SBSD_SBSH_ID and D.SBSH_STATUS < 8) and ( E.SCPC_DAYS_FROM > 0 and days(B.INVS_EXPECTEDPAYMENTDATE) - days(A.INSP_FINANCEDATE) between E.SCPC_DAYS_FROM and E.SCPC_DAYS_UNTIL and ':6' = 'N' or (E.SCPC_DAYS_FROM = 0 or ':6' = 'Y') ) order by A.INSP_FINANCEDATE for fetch only
